{
  "manifest": {
    "id": "gh",
    "name": {
      "default": "GitHub PRs",
      "zh": "GitHub PR 看板"
    },
    "description": {
      "default": "Review queue + my open PRs，via `gh search prs --json`"
    },
    "docs": "# GitHub PR 看板\n\n本地化的 PR review / 我的 PR 列表。数据通过 `gh` CLI 同步进来。\n\n## 工作流\n\n```sh\ncorelet scheduler tick           # 内部：gh search prs --review-requested=@me / --author=@me\n                            # → 写到本 miniapp 的 prs 集合\n```\n\n## Tabs\n\n- **Review**：被 request review 的 open PR（`reviewed_by_me=true`）\n- **我的**：我写的 open PR（`authored_by_me=true`）\n- **全部**：所有 open PR\n\n## 同 PR 多分类\n\n一个 PR 可能同时是 review queue 和 mine（自己 author 自己 review）。schema 用两个 bool 字段而非 category 字符串，ingest dedup 时 merge 旗标。\n\n## 不写入字段\n\n这是只读看板：Agent 写库，用户只浏览 + 跳 GitHub。\n",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "runtime": "json-ui-react-v2",
    "permissions": [
      "data:read",
      "data:write",
      "notifications:post"
    ],
    "window": {
      "style": "phone",
      "width": 440,
      "height": 880
    },
    "background": {
      "js_path": "gh.background.js"
    },
    "collections": {
      "prs": {
        "schema": {
          "pr_id": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "number": {
            "type": "number"
          },
          "title": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "url": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "repo": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "author": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "state": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "is_draft": {
            "type": "boolean"
          },
          "reviewed_by_me": {
            "type": "boolean"
          },
          "authored_by_me": {
            "type": "boolean"
          },
          "comments_count": {
            "type": "number"
          },
          "labels": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "updated_at": {
            "type": "string"
          }
        },
        "indexes": [
          "pr_id",
          "reviewed_by_me",
          "authored_by_me",
          "state",
          "updated_at"
        ]
      }
    }
  },
  "ui": "gh.ui.tsx"
}
